# Third-Party Notices

This project relies on several open source packages. 
Detailed licensing notices for these packages are implicitly derived from their repositories and will be appended here upon major builds or releases.

### Flutter / Dart
Packages resolved via pub.dev are governed by the dependencies logged in `apps/flutter/pubspec.lock`.

### Rust (Cargo)
Crates resolved via Cargo are governed by the dependencies logged in `Cargo.lock`. 
The repository employs `cargo-deny` to ensure only OSI-approved permissive licenses (like MIT and Apache-2.0) are utilized internally, preventing conflicts with the primary project license.
